#  ( (word) )
word_space<-DF %>% 
  unnest_tokens(input=content,
                output = word,
                token="words")

#  
word_space<-word_space %>% 
  mutate(word=str_replace_all(word, "[^-]", " "), #    .  .
         word=str_squish(word))

#

  count(President, word) %>% 
  filter(str_count(word)>1)

(5) . RR(relative risk ) RR(log relative risk) 10 . (10)

#   
frequency<-speeches %>% 
  count(President, word) %>% 
  filter(str_count(word)>1)

#       
frequency_wide <- frequency %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = President,
              values_from = n,
              values_fill = list(n = 0)) %>% 
  mutate(ratio_noe = ((+ 1)/(sum( + 1))), #     
         ratio_lee = (( + 1)/(sum( + 1))), #     
         rr = ratio_noe/ratio_lee, # (RR)  
         log_rr = log((( + 1)/(sum( + 1)))/
                        (( + 1)/(sum( + 1))))) %>% 
  dplyr::select(-,-) %>% 
  arrange(-log_rr)
